-- Lehman executives including Fuld subpoenaed: report
-- 
-- Fri Oct 17, 2008 7:16am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/17/us-lehmanbrothers-idUSTRE49G2X920081017

 

 (Reuters) - Prosecutors have subpoenaed a dozen executives of Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc LEHMQ.PK including Chief Executive Dick Fuld in connection with three grand jury probes investigating the fall of the investment bank, the New York Post reported. 

 Calls made to Lehman Brothers seeking comment were not immediately returned. (Reporting by Shradhha Sharma in Bangalore; Editing by  Andrew Callus )